{"tid":1079828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【話變就變】廣電總局受群眾壓力 限古令即時解封","createTime":"2019-03-27T07:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T08:01:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44fea08b2ff3728124cef1245506a2536074ea23","tid":1079828,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"大陸廣電總局上周下達「限古令」，只要是武俠、玄幻、歷史、神話、穿越、宮鬥的古裝戲禁播到6月，但官方未想到業內和觀眾反應如此大，網民都鬧爆（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2THJFA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2THJFA4&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5XdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=e5fdb113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2THJFA4</a> ）。日前廣電總局網絡司分別召集3家平台，當3家平台簽下保證書後，古裝劇4月可逐步上線，換言之，古裝劇解封了。<br />\n保證書內提到解封的條件，包括每月15日前網路平台要通過廣電總局交代每月上線的古裝劇列表，還有現實題材要佔年度60%、以及未拿到上線許可的古裝劇，一律不能提前排播或宣傳，而參與會議的3家最大平台都寫了保證書。所以之前被禁的《新白娘子傳奇》，今日公佈重新定檔下月3日於愛奇藝播出。首度拍攝電視劇的章子怡與楊祐寧演出的《帝凰業》也重新安排播映。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190327/59417673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59417673&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5XdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=3abf0507\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190327%2F59417673&h=c335bb6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190327/59417673</a>"},{"pid":"1a01f06f2db52608b1a261160f0711233bfeb20f","tid":1079828,"uid":95,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"朝令夕改，亡國不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb33a7b86201f75a3ed700674eae51203856d0b","tid":1079828,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a01f06f2db52608b1a261160f0711233bfeb20f","tid":1079828,"uid":95,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"朝令夕改，亡國不遠了<im